Like prior Saints Row games, it is the story missions that are the best part of the game. Saints Row 4 features some incredible story missions that revolve around the Boss rescuing the other Saints trapped in their own person prisons within the simulation. This structure allows Volition to get creative and bizarre with the types, structure and look of missions. Most relate directly to the character’s deepest fear, so things get weird, drinking donkey beer on satan’s ladder weird.
